name: Fidelity Global Equity+ Balanced Fund
longDescription: The Fund invests primarily in a mix of equity securities and an expansive set of fixed income securities of U.S. issuers and other issuers located anywhere in the world. It can invest in these securities either directly or indirectly through investments in underlying funds, which may include liquid alternative mutual funds.
